abstract: Robert Allenby withdraws from Canadian Open with two-stroke lead after splitting with caddie Mick Middlemo in first round; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Robert Allenby withdrew from the Canadian Open in Oakville, Ontario, after splitting with his caddie, Mick Middlemo, in the first round. Chad Campbell held a two-stroke lead at nine-under 63.

headline.main: Robert Allenby Withdraws in First Round
